124
0:10:19,206 --> 0:10:23,567
Today, everything in that direction might look alien and hostile,


125
0:10:23,567 --> 0:10:25,287
but 50,000 years ago


126
0:10:25,287 --> 0:10:28,407
it was Europe, the land that lay ahead,


127
0:10:28,407 --> 0:10:37,606
which would be more dangerous than they could ever have imagined.


128
0:10:37,606 --> 0:10:40,647
