227
0:18:20,446 --> 0:18:23,326
so he looks quite human.


228
0:18:23,326 --> 0:18:26,567
Would you notice him walking along in the street?


229
0:18:26,567 --> 0:18:29,166
But then there are things which do look a bit odd.


230
0:18:29,166 --> 0:18:31,366
The distance between his eyes.


231
0:18:31,366 --> 0:18:33,446
The breadth of his nose, just here.


232
0:18:33,446 --> 0:18:35,527
That looks a bit strange.


233
0:18:35,527 --> 0:18:39,247
And he's got this amazing brow ridge.


234
0:18:39,247 --> 0:18:45,366
It really sticks out over his eyes.


235
0:18:45,366 --> 0:18:48,366
Neanderthals are our distant cousins.


236
0:18:48,366 --> 0:18:50,7
their ancestors reached Europe


237
0:18:50,7 --> 0:18:54,686
hundreds of thousands of years before us.


238
0:18:54,686 --> 0:18:57,47
they spread across a huge region,


239
0:18:57,47 --> 0:19:1,606
from Siberia to Spain.


240
0:19:1,606 --> 0:19:6,406
