273
0:21:0,807 --> 0:21:4,366
So this would have been a person who was much more heavily muscled,


274
0:21:4,366 --> 0:21:12,487
generally much more rugged-looking than us today.


275
0:21:12,487 --> 0:21:31,926
they would have been formidable competitors.


276
0:21:31,926 --> 0:21:35,926
The Neanderthals were tougher and better cold-adapted than us,


277
0:21:35,926 --> 0:21:39,807
